content: A photo from a walk on 2025-03-29.

photos.alt: A photo of a courtyard as seen from over a top of a door in a hedge. There is a single tree in the middle, with some plants here and there, potted and not. The sun is shining brightly, the tree in the middle leaves a shadow, the leaves of the hedge are forming a frame around the photo with out-of-focus leaves.
